Rating: 3
I made this the other night and have been dreaming about it ever since. I didn't have the fresh chilies, so I used the red chili paste..srichaca or whatever it is. I peeled and deveined the shrimp, but otherwise followed the recipe..except I don't use fresh lemongrass. I love the lemongrass that comes in a tube (can also get cilantro and basil in the tube). They taste great and I always have that ingredient on hand. I used extra lemongrass. Everybody loved it including my picky kids. My husband thought it tasted "very Thai".

