I boiled 4lb. tiger shrimp then cooled in ice water. I peeled the shrimp leaving the tails on.I only doubled the rest of the recipe due to no shells. then let marinate for 3 or 4 hours.Used thai basil for mint and some cannola oil to make things stick. Brought to wine dinner and it disappeared.Verygood.

