Delicious, easy, and healthy! The chillies make quite a spicy sauce, but don't worry - once the shrimp are shelled, it's not too hot. Also, I added fresh pineapple chunks to the salad bed which added a nice fresh balance to the spice. I prefer the pineapple to tomato. Serves 2 as a wonderful light summer meal.

